organic.title: Enloe Medical Center
organic.snippet: Enloe Health is a nonprofit hospital in Chico, CA, with a Level II Trauma Center. It's rated 'A' for safety and offers maternity, cardiac, and cancer care.

organic.title: Welcome to Enloe Health | Enloe Health | Chico, CA
organic.snippet: Enloe Health rebranded with new values: safety, engagement, trust, excellence, and belonging. The logo honors Dr. Enloe and his log ambulance. They offer 45+ medical services.

organic.title: Chico – Springfield Drive - Nvih.org
organic.snippet: NVIH Children's Health Center at 1515 Springfield Drive, Chico, CA offers medical, behavioral, and community health for ages birth-18. Open Mon-Fri, 8am-5pm. Call 530-781-1440.
